definitions.definition: A child who is able to creep using its hands and knees but is not able to walk.
A tractor crawler, a motorized vehicle that uses caterpillar tracks instead of wheels .
( Internet ) A software bot that autonomously follows connected paths such as links between web pages .
A mobile stage in the development of stationary hemipteran insects such as scale insects —generally the first instar .
( UK , slang , obsolete ) A cab that is driven slowly along while its driver looks out for a fare .

definitions.definition: A person who is abused , physically or verbally , and returns to the abuser a supplicant .
